Administer Social Customer Service

Enable social customer service in your organization and customize your support agents' experience.

Social Customer Service is available in all editions with the Service Cloud. To administer Social Customer Service: 
Manage Users and Customize Application are needed.
To create case feed items: Feed Tracking for All Related Objects on the Case object, to make attachment download links public: Create Public Links.

There are considerations when adjusting the default setup. Automated users need access to posts, and custom validation rules should ensure all users involved have necessary permissions.

Set Up Social Customer Service
Enable Social Customer Service, sync your social accounts, configure post handling, and assign social handles.
How to Reconnect a Social Account
Reconnect your social account for Social Customer Service.
Tour the Social Conversations Component
When you add the component, agents can quickly get a sense of who the customer is.

Configure the Social Conversations Component
Use the Lightning App Builder to set up the component.
Enable Social Post Approvals
Social care agents are problem solvers and voice of your brand on social networks. Enable moderation for social customer service.
Enable Service Post Reply Without a Case
No need to open a case just to thank customers on their social network of choice.

Create the Social Action Interface
The social action is created when you install Social Customer Service. Format Case Content from Social Posts and Modify the Default Apex Class are also available.
